# T-13 (docs/THREAT_MODEL.md): minimum release age ("cooldown").
# Do not install a package version published less than 7 days ago, so a freshly
# published malicious release is not pulled before the community detects and
# yanks it. Honored by npm >= 11.10 (silently ignored by older npm); gates
# `npm install` / `npm update` resolution — frozen `npm ci` is unaffected.
min-release-age=7
